w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/TheLastDinnerParty-hype-buzzy-band-interview-story-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/TheLastDinnerParty-hype-buzzy-band-interview-story-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/TheLastDinnerParty-hype-buzzy-band-interview-story-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/TheLastDinnerParty-hype-buzzy-band-interview-story-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-last-dinner-party">最后的晚宴派对</a>表示，他们在反思如何成为年度最受关注的摇滚乐队时，“试图忽略‘炒作’和‘热闹乐队’这两个词”。</p><p>这支伦敦乐队和<a href="https://www.nme.com/blogs/nme-radar/the-nme-100-essential-emerging-artists-for-2023-radar-3372061">NME 100</a>校友将于 2 月 2 日通过 Island 发行他们的首张专辑<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-last-dinner-party-announce-debut-album-prelude-to-ecstasy-release-new-single-on-your-side-listen-preorder-3528044">《Prelude To Ecstasy》</a> （<a href="https://tldp.lnk.to/preludetoecstasyPR" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在此预订</a>）。它将收录 2023 年的单曲<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-last-dinner-party-shares-smashing-debut-single-nothing-matters-radar-3433299">《Nothing Matters》</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-last-dinner-party-new-single-sinner-uk-tour-radar-3463558">《Sinner》</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-last-dinner-party-share-new-single-my-lady-of-mercy-3511842">《My Lady Of Mercy》</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-last-dinner-party-announce-debut-album-prelude-to-ecstasy-release-new-single-on-your-side-listen-preorder-3528044#:~:text=The%20Last%20Dinner%20Party%20have,%2Fpre%2Dsave%20here).">《On Your Side》</a> 。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/the-cover/the-cover-the-last-dinner-party-interview-prelude-to-ecstasy-3552625">最后的晚宴：巴洛克流行音乐的新加冕君主</a></strong></li></ul><p>最近， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/brit-awards-announce-rising-star-shortlist-for-2024-3550021">The Last Evening Party 获得全英新星奖提名</a>，并<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/check-out-the-bbc-sound-of-2024-longlist-3552812">出现在 BBC Sound Of 2024 长名单</a>以及<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/blur-and-boygenius-lead-bbc-radio-6-musics-inaugural-artists-of-the-year-3532161">BBC Radio 6 Music 年度艺术家名单</a>中。乐队的首张单曲《Nothing Matters》也在<a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-features/best-songs-of-2023-3-3551141"><em>NME</em>的“2023 年 50 首最佳歌曲”排行榜</a>上名列第五。</p><p>在<a href="https://www.nme.com/features/the-cover/the-cover-the-last-dinner-party-interview-prelude-to-ecstasy-3552625"><em>《NME</em> 》《The Cover》的一次新采访</a>中，五人畅谈了他们目前的经历以及在音乐领域的崛起“感觉有点像开车开得很快，却无法掌控方向盘” 。</p><p>主唱阿比盖尔·莫里斯继续说道：“我们试图忽略‘炒作’和‘热闹乐队’这些词，只专注于我们的基础：演奏、创作和排练我们的音乐。”</p><p>乔治亚·戴维斯（男低音）说：“耶稣掌舵（笑）。”她解释说，TLDP“花了很长时间才发布任何东西，这在某种程度上是故意的”，并补充道：“这是关于整个体验，而不是来自单身人士的即时认可。”</p><p>后来，乐队触及了<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-last-dinner-party-respond-to-industry-plant-allegations-nme-radar-3436536">他们是“工业工厂”的错误假设</a>。 “我们必须解决这个问题吗？”莫里斯向<em>NME</em>询问。戴维斯也表示：“我们认为这是一种恭维。如果人们认为这好得令人难以置信，那么我们只能说谢谢。” </p><figure id="attachment_3550937" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3550937" style="width: 2160px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3550937" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/NME-COVER-THE-LAST-DINNER-PARTY-CREDIT-PHOEBE-FOX@2160x2700.jpg" alt="NME 封面上的最后晚宴，摄影：Phoebe Fox" width="2160" height="2700" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/NME-COVER-THE-LAST-DINNER-PARTY-CREDIT-PHOEBE-FOX@2160x2700.jpg 2160w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/NME-COVER-THE-LAST-DINNER-PARTY-CREDIT-PHOEBE-FOX@2160x2700-400x500.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/NME-COVER-THE-LAST-DINNER-PARTY-CREDIT-PHOEBE-FOX@2160x2700-800x1000.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/NME-COVER-THE-LAST-DINNER-PARTY-CREDIT-PHOEBE-FOX@2160x2700-696x870.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/NME-COVER-THE-LAST-DINNER-PARTY-CREDIT-PHOEBE-FOX@2160x2700-1392x1740.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/NME-COVER-THE-LAST-DINNER-PARTY-CREDIT-PHOEBE-FOX@2160x2700-1068x1335.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2160px) 100vw, 2160px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3550937" class="wp-caption-text"> NME 封面上的最后晚宴。图片来源：NME 的菲比·福克斯</figcaption></figure><p>在谈话的其他地方，这位音乐家表示最后的晚宴派对“知道他们与其他从事后朋克音乐的乐队不同”。莫里斯解释道：“我们想象了外出时希望看到的那种快乐、激动人心的表演，并据此创建了我们自己的‘梦想乐队’。”</p><p>该乐队<a href="https://www.nme.com/glastonbury">在格拉斯顿伯里</a>首次亮相并于今年<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-last-dinner-party-announces-first-ever-north-american-tour-buy-tickets-3499834">开始了首次北美巡演</a>，他们还谈到了在发布音乐之前在现场磨练技艺的重要性。</p><p> “我们的朋友和家人在我们最初的几场演出后实际上就回来了，而不是找借口不回来，”主音吉他手艾米丽·罗伯茨回忆道。 “那时我们就知道我们很好。”</p><p>莫里斯告诉<em>《NME》</em> ：“从一开始，在我们进行一次排练之前，我们就决定我们的视觉效果和音乐一样重要。我们希望整个事情成为一个完整的奇观。” </p><figure id="attachment_3552664" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3552664" style="width: 2560px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3552664" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/NME-COVER-THE-LAST-DINNER-PARTY-HERO-CREDIT-PHOEBE-FOX@2560x1625.jpg" alt="最后的晚宴" width="2560" height="1625" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/NME-COVER-THE-LAST-DINNER-PARTY-HERO-CREDIT-PHOEBE-FOX@2560x1625.jpg 2560w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/NME-COVER-THE-LAST-DINNER-PARTY-HERO-CREDIT-PHOEBE-FOX@2560x1625-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/NME-COVER-THE-LAST-DINNER-PARTY-HERO-CREDIT-PHOEBE-FOX@2560x1625-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/NME-COVER-THE-LAST-DINNER-PARTY-HERO-CREDIT-PHOEBE-FOX@2560x1625-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/NME-COVER-THE-LAST-DINNER-PARTY-HERO-CREDIT-PHOEBE-FOX@2560x1625-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/NME-COVER-THE-LAST-DINNER-PARTY